headline: Dow Jones Futures Fall After Market Reverses Higher; Meta Deal Lifts Nvidia, Hits AI Rivals
summary: The still-divided stock market reversed higher for slim gains Tuesday. Nvidia rose late on a Meta AI deal, but AMD and Broadcom slumped.

headline: Monster Beverage, Stock Of The Day, Near Buy Point As Growth Accelerates
summary: Monster Beverage's earnings and sales growth are ramping up for the energy drinks giant. MNST stock is near a buy point after trading tightly.
